==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Scavenger hunt
<hw>Scav"en*ger hunt</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>a game in
which individuals or teams are given a list of items and must go out,
gather them together without purchasing them, and bring them back; the
first person or team to return with the complete list is the winner. The
items are sometimes common but often of a humorous sort.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scavenging</ent>⟦br⟧
